Grammar

    0 $accept: Tiny $end

    1 Tiny: PROGRAM Name ':' Dclns Body Name '.'

    2 Dclns: VAR Dclns_1
    3      | ε

    4 Dclns_1: ε
    5        | Dcln ';' Dclns_1

    6 Dcln: NameList ':' Type

    7 NameList: Name
    8         | NameList ',' Name

    9 Type: INTEGER
   10     | BOOLEAN

   11 Body: BEGINX StmtList END

   12 StmtList: Statement
   13         | StmtList ';' Statement

   14 Statement: Name ASSIGNMENT Expression
   15          | OUTPUT '(' Expression ')'
   16          | IF Expression THEN Statement ELSE Statement
   17          | WHILE Expression DO Statement
   18          | Body
   19          | ε

   20 Expression: AddTerm
   21           | AddTerm '=' AddTerm
   22           | AddTerm NE AddTerm
   23           | AddTerm '<' AddTerm
   24           | AddTerm '>' AddTerm
   25           | AddTerm LTE AddTerm
   26           | AddTerm GE AddTerm

   27 AddTerm: MulTerm
   28        | AddTerm '+' MulTerm
   29        | AddTerm '-' MulTerm
   30        | AddTerm OR MulTerm

   31 MulTerm: PowTerm
   32        | MulTerm '*' PowTerm
   33        | MulTerm '/' PowTerm
   34        | MulTerm AND PowTerm
   35        | MulTerm MOD PowTerm

   36 PowTerm: UnaryTerm
   37        | UnaryTerm EXP PowTerm

   38 UnaryTerm: Primary
   39          | '-' UnaryTerm
   40          | '+' UnaryTerm
   41          | NOT UnaryTerm

   42 Primary: READ
   43        | Name
   44        | INTEGER_NUM
   45        | '(' Expression ')'

   46 Name: IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '(' (40) 15 45
    ')' (41) 15 45
    '*' (42) 32
    '+' (43) 28 40
    ',' (44) 8
    '-' (45) 29 39
    '.' (46) 1
    '/' (47) 33
    ':' (58) 1 6
    ';' (59) 5 13
    '<' (60) 23
    '=' (61) 21
    '>' (62) 24
    error (256)
    END <info> (258) 11
    VAR <info> (259) 2
    IDENTIFIER <info> (260) 46
    IF <info> (261) 16
    READ <info> (262) 42
    ELSE <info> (263) 16
    THEN <info> (264) 16
    NE <info> (265) 22
    MOD <info> (266) 35
    WHILE <info> (267) 17
    OUTPUT <info> (268) 15
    NOT <info> (269) 41
    DO <info> (270) 17
    BEGINX <info> (271) 11
    BOOLEAN <info> (272) 10
    INTEGER_NUM <info> (273) 44
    AND <info> (274) 34
    INTEGER <info> (275) 9
    EXP <info> (276) 37
    LTE <info> (277) 25
    GE <info> (278) 26
    OR <info> (279) 30
    ASSIGNMENT <info> (280) 14
    PROGRAM <info> (281) 1


